{"tid":1365648,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【7.21地鐵不合作運動】白衫鄉黑跳閘入元朗站，無畀錢，好驚7.27會重演","createTime":"2019-07-25T16:51:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T16:51:51.000Z","uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"43ae1a8fcc1e62474a647544a2c55afe758a1e67","tid":1365648,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:51:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ts1u5X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ts1u5X.jpg&h=34d24922&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7月21日，大批白衫鄉黑跳閘衝入元朗站，沒有付錢，港鐵職員完全無制止。我強烈譴責此行為，根據港鐵附例，無付足車票，要罰$500。白衫黨仲周街貼標語，連罰$1500都唔驚，唔怪得佢地敢搭地鐵唔畀錢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽講7.21有旺角白衫入元朗打人，計返車費$20，即係每25個人捉到1個，地鐵就要蝕錢，仲衰過阻地鐵開車、阻人返工班示威者。<br />\n<br />\n我上網搵到，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">原來白衫黨係學法國黃背心「接管或燒毀道路收費站，讓汽車自由通行，令政府無利可圖。」</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/06/14/lessons-from-the-yellow-vests/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F14%2Flessons-from-the-yellow-vests%2F&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hIjkqoP0ISDA%2F8fQ3RVu%2FF4%3D&h=db98902b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/06/14/lessons-from-the-yellow-vests/</a><br />\n<br />\n我好驚7.27同樣會有白衫鄉黑搭車唔畀錢，希望連登仔約埋喺閘口譴責佢地，同埋向查飛男神女神舉報。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}